            {
              "id": "CVE-2026-11352",
              "name": "OsPackageVulnerability",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "curl: libcurl: curl/libcurl: Remote denial of service via QUIC UDP receive function vulnerability"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "An issue in curl’s QUIC UDP receive function allows a malicious HTTP/3 server\nto trigger a remote denial of service against a curl or libcurl client.\nBecause the helper function discards zero-length UDP datagrams before counting\nthem toward the per-call packet budget, a connected QUIC peer can continuously\nstream empty datagrams to indefinitely stall the client."
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "error"
              },
              "helpUri": "https://avd.aquasec.com/nvd/cve-2026-11352",
              "help": {
                "text": "Vulnerability CVE-2026-11352\nSeverity: HIGH\nPackage: libcurl\nFixed Version: \nLink: [CVE-2026-11352](https://avd.aquasec.com/nvd/cve-2026-11352)\nAn issue in curl’s QUIC UDP receive function allows a malicious HTTP/3 server\nto trigger a remote denial of service against a curl or libcurl client.\nBecause the helper function discards zero-length UDP datagrams before counting\nthem toward the per-call packet budget, a connected QUIC peer can continuously\nstream empty datagrams to indefinitely stall the client.",
                "markdown": "**Vulnerability CVE-2026-11352**\n| Severity | Package | Fixed Version | Link |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n|HIGH|libcurl||[CVE-2026-11352](https://avd.aquasec.com/nvd/cve-2026-11352)|\n\nAn issue in curl’s QUIC UDP receive function allows a malicious HTTP/3 server\nto trigger a remote denial of service against a curl or libcurl client.\nBecause the helper function discards zero-length UDP datagrams before counting\nthem toward the per-call packet budget, a connected QUIC peer can continuously\nstream empty datagrams to indefinitely stall the client."
              },
              "properties": {
                "cvssv3_baseScore": 7.5,
