              "id": "CVE-2026-8925",
              "name": "OsPackageVulnerability",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "curl: curl: Double-free vulnerability in SASL authentication"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "The curl logic that works with SASL authentication could end up cleaning up\nthe GSASL context *twice* without clearing the pointer in between, making it\n`free()` the same pointer twice."
