            {
              "id": "CVE-2026-11856",
              "name": "OsPackageVulnerability",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "curl: curl: Information disclosure via incorrect Digest authentication header reuse"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Successfully using libcurl to do a transfer to a specific HTTP origin\n(`hostA`) with **Digest** authentication and then changing the origin to a\ndifferent one (`hostB`) for a second transfer, reusing the same handle, makes\nlibcurl wrongly pass on the  `Authorization:` header field meant for `hostA`,\nto `hostB`."
