              "id": "CVE-2026-7168",
              "name": "OsPackageVulnerability",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "curl: libcurl: Information disclosure via incorrect Proxy-Authorization header reuse"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Successfully using libcurl to do a transfer over a specific HTTP proxy\n(`proxyA`) with **Digest** authentication and then changing the proxy host to\na second one (`proxyB`) for a second transfer, reusing the same handle, makes\nlibcurl wrongly pass on the `Proxy-Authorization:` header field meant for\n`proxyA`, to `proxyB`."
