              "name": "OsPackageVulnerability",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "curl: curl: Information disclosure via incorrect .netrc password lookup"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "When asking curl to use a `.netrc` file to find credentials and at the same\ntime specifying a URL with a username(without a password), like\n`https://user@example.com/`, curl could wrongly get and use the password for\n*another* user set in the `.netrc` file for that host if such a one exists and\nthere is no match for the specified user."
