              "id": "CVE-2024-38820",
              "name": "LanguageSpecificPackageVulnerability",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "The fix for CVE-2022-22968 made disallowedFieldspatterns in DataBinder ..."
              },
              "fullDescription": {
